<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-07T11:09:45-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-07T11:09:45-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T11:09:45-05:00</updated><title>索尼声称其最新的 A9 III 无反光镜相机解决了卷帘快门问题</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VCxzqQL9AEP-7O1vrke_Z2se-iE=/0x134:4652x3235/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image /image/72838682/ILCE_9M3_front_.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;索尼 A9 III 在全画幅无反光镜相机中配备了该公司首款全局快门。&lt;/em>; |图片：索尼&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;EER6XD&quot;>;索尼宣布推出其广受欢迎的专业无反光镜相机系列中的最新产品：A9 III。这是一款售价 5,999 美元的全画幅相机，配备堆叠式 24.6 兆像素传感器，成功&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/3/20896423/sony-a9-ii-mirrorless-camera-announced -specs-price-release-date&quot;>;四年前发布的 A9 II&lt;/a>;。但 A9 III 最重要的是它的新快门。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;F7uTyW&quot;>;A9 III 是第一款使用全局快门的全画幅相机。这使得它可以同时曝光每个像素，因此静态图像和视频都不会失真。大多数无反光镜相机（例如佳能 R5、松下 GH5 和尼康 Z9）都配备卷帘快门。卷帘快门通过逐行曝光像素来捕获图像，这可能会导致失真。下面是来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lensrentals.com/blog/2021/07/understanding-the-difference-in-global-and-rolling-shutters/&quot;>;Lensrentals.com&lt;/a 的图表>; 很好地显示了这种差异。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; ...&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/ 7/23950504/sony-a9-iii-mirrorless-camera-global-shutter-price-release&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950504/sony-a9-iii-mirrorless-camera-global-shutter-price-release" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950504/sony-a9-iii-mirrorless-camera-global-shutter-price-release</id><author><name>贝卡·法尔萨斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T11:04:25-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T11:04:25-05:00</updated><title>这个智能车库门控制器不再很智能</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ew5v-zpVKWx3jDZ10nVC8j6IVEU=/743x116:4968x2933/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /72838660/8A0A0362.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Chamberlain MyQ 智能车库门控制器连接到车库门开启器，以便您可以从任何地方控制它。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NcWUzj&quot;>;The Chamberlain Group — MyQ 智能车库门控制器技术的所有者 — 拥有&lt;a href=&quot;https://chamberlaingroup. com/press/a-message-about-our-decision-to-prevent-unauthorized-usage-of-myq&quot;>;宣布关闭&lt;/a>;对其 API 的所有“未经授权的访问”。此举打破了成千上万依赖 &lt;a href=&quot;https://homebridge.io/&quot;>;Homebridge&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge 等平台的用户的智能家居集成.com/23744526/smart-home-assistant-how-to-automation&quot;>;家庭助理&lt;/a>;可以执行一些操作，例如在锁上前门时关闭车库门，或者在门打开 10 秒后闪烁灯光等分钟，或者他们想要用他们购买和付费的设备进行的任何其他控制或自动化。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ut5aiq&quot;>;这一举动发生在张伯伦一年后&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/8/23/23318157/chamberlain-myq-home-bridge- hub-discontinued-homekit&quot;>;停止与官方 Apple HomeKit 集成&lt;/a>;，几个月后它最终终止了对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5google.com/2023/06/16/chamberlain-myq- 的支持google-assistant-discontinued/&quot;>;Google 助理&lt;/a>;。可悲的是，这是该公司如何继续敌视......的另一个例子&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23949612/chamberlain-myq-smart-garage-door -controller-homebridge-integrations&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23949612/chamberlain-myq-smart-garage-door-controller-homebridge-integrations" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23949612/chamberlain-myq-smart-garage-door-controller-homebridge-integrations</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T11:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T11:00:00-05:00</updated><title> YouTube的广告拦截打击面临新挑战：隐私法</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;抽象背景上的 YouTube 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/huTWYJs8WnnNFWt6E4JwAoDFFzI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/72838616/acastro_STK092_02.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;kpyTkU&quot;>;随着 YouTube 收紧对广告拦截器的限制，欧盟的隐私倡导者押注政府法规可以阻止镇压。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HWk91n&quot;>;隐私专家 Alexander Hanff，&lt;a href=&quot;https://isp.page/news/privacy-advocate-challenges-youtubes-ad-blocking-detection/&quot;>; 10 月向爱尔兰数据保护委员会 (DPC) 提出投诉&lt;/a>;。汉夫认为，YouTube 的广告拦截器检测系统侵犯了隐私（谷歌否认了这一指控），并且根据欧盟法律是非法的。 “AdBlock 检测脚本是间谍软件——没有其他方法可以描述它们，因此未经同意就部署它们是不可接受的，”Hanff 告诉 &lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>;。 “我认为在大多数情况下，部署任何可用于监视我的设备的技术都是不道德且非法的。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;VgeFQy&quot;>;与广告拦截器的斗争...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950513/youtube-ad-blocker-crackdown-privacy-advocates-eu&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950513/youtube-ad-blocker-crackdown-privacy-advocates-eu" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950513/youtube-ad-blocker-crackdown-privacy-advocates-eu</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T11:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T11:00:00-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/a9DFjTwteBiMbEI8chPLU5J-fiw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72838629/236830_MAIN_Gift_Guide_LEDE_STILL_CVir吉尼亚.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;一系列伟大的科技和非科技礼物，旨在送给我们所有人中的修补匠、创意者和孩子。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>边缘人员</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T10:30:43-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T10:30:43-05:00</updated><title>谷歌承包商反对阅读淫秽的巴德提示——现在他们正在组建工会</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 文字标记的插图，以深蓝色背景上的红色和粉色书写。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/oujk0EL30p7xRdxOB1x8sycXJcs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72838472/STK093_Google_06.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pf5TUo&quot;>;一群 Google 合同工，帮助培训公司的 Bard AI 聊天机器人并撰写 Google 帮助文章&lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.alphabetworkersunion.org/press/google-help-workers-triumph-with-alphabet-workers-union-cwa-election-victory-despite-retaliatory-actions-by-google-and-accenture&quot;>;以压倒性多数投票通过周一工会&lt;/a>;。这些通过埃森哲签约为 Google 工作的工人成立了工会，以确保更好的工作条件和保护。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;RV3r6W&quot;>;承包商将加入代表 Google 员工的劳工组织 Alphabet 工人工会。谷歌及其 Alphabet 母公司。他们在六月被指示从事当时尚未宣布的 Bard 聊天机器人工作后，首次开始了工会工作。作为帮助训练机器人的努力的一部分，他们被要求“处理淫秽、图形和攻击性提示”，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-06-08/ google-contract-staff-that-helped-train-ai-seek-to-unionize?sref=ExbtjcSG&quot;>;根据&lt;em>;彭博&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;的报告。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;JYxwON&quot;>;当其中一名承包商提交...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950392/google-contractors-accenture- obscene-bard-prompts-unionizing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950392/google-contractors-accenture-obscene-bard-prompts-unionizing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950392/google-contractors-accenture-obscene-bard-prompts-unionizing</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T10:06:20-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T10:06:20-05:00</updated><title>零摩托车扩大阵容，着眼于引进新骑手</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;零S电动摩托车&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RAji0I6QQRuhHcFtKzU-Hu67z-A=/0x0:4674x3116/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/72838364/MY24_S_Action_1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图像：零&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;YApDEm&quot;>;零摩托车确实倾向于它的&lt;a href= “https://www.forbes.com/sites/hannahelliott/2014/06/24/meet-the-latest-from-the-tesla-of-motorcycles-the-zero-sr-streetfighter/?sh=6d6d96e04394” >;被誉为“摩托车界的特斯拉”。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;t7ii4Q&quot;>;该公司是该国领先的电动摩托车制造商之一，今天宣布推出两款新车型：配备全新电机的 Model S 街头自行车；以及两款新的运动车型：DS 和 DSR 车型。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6DVbE8&quot;>;这家总部位于加州的公司旨在通过降低价格和性能等准入门槛来吸引新乘客，希望增加愿意花数万美元购买的人数在电池供电的两轮车上。随着过去二十年新摩托车购买量基本上翻了一番，Zero 认为可以通过增加其已经令人印象深刻的摩托车阵容来吸引这些新骑手。 &lt;/p>; &lt;h3 id=&quot;aWwuDK&quot;>;Z...&lt;/h3>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949263/zero-motorcycles- model-s-ds-dsr-price-specs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949263/zero-motorcycles-model-s-ds-dsr-price-specs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949263/zero-motorcycles-model-s-ds-dsr-price-specs</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T10:00:40-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T10:00:40-05:00</updated><title> Epic 诉 Google 的审判可能会归结为简单与复杂</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google Play 徽标内 Epic Games 徽标和 Google 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_cnYnnGh5J0lRD8BYC9gNKftxY0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72838342/236883_Epic_Vs_Google_B_CVirginia.0 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;在开场陈述中，谷歌试图概述其 Android 业务的目标。 Epic 专注于将这家科技巨头描绘成恶霸。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949849/epic-google-trial-day-one -recap-summary&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949849/epic-google-trial-day-one-recap-summary" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949849/epic-google-trial-day-one-recap-summary</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T10:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T10:00:00-05:00</updated><title>巴拉克·奥巴马谈人工智能、言论自由和互联网的未来</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/exWjMYQ6_DoUatBxuFKEkydTcUs=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72838297 /Obama_Decoder.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;这位前总统在 Decoder 上与我一起讨论人工智能监管、第一修正案，当然还有他的主屏幕上有哪些应用程序。&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23948871/barack-obama-ai-regulation-free-speech-first-amendment-decoder-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23948871/barack-obama-ai-regulation-free-speech-first-amendment-decoder-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23948871/barack-obama-ai-regulation-free-speech-first-amendment-decoder-interview</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T09:10:32-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T09:10:32-05:00</updated><title> 2023 年 Netflix 极客周的所有重大新闻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个秃头男孩，头上装饰着巨大的蓝色箭头纹身。男孩穿着橙色连身裤般的服装，搭配短斗篷。男孩还拿着一根木杖，伸出来他腾出手来防守，站在冰冻的苔原上。” src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lOHyqXcPdunjWi-Y3-29M3raNX8=/5x0:3596x2394/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72834325/AVTR_101_Unit_01655.0。 jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;戈登·科米尔 (Gordon Cormier) 在《阿凡达：最后的气宗》中饰演安昂&lt;/em>;。&lt;em>;。&lt;/em>; |图片：Netflix&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;《阿凡达：最后的气宗》、《斯科特朝圣者起飞》、《鬼泣》、《怪奇物语》和《3 Body Problem》都在 Netflix 的 Geeked 2023 展示会上放映。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23948622/netflix-geeked-week-2023-stranger-things-5-avatar-last-airbender-3-body-problem&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23948622/netflix-geeked-week-2023-stranger-things-5-avatar-last-airbender-3-body-problem" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23948622/netflix-geeked-week-2023-stranger-things-5-avatar-last-airbender-3-body-problem</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>前 Kotaku 作家正在推出一个新的视频游戏网站——这次他们拥有它</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;The Aftermath 标志。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xZ9oV1ZEGA_7MEwHuX9AaFORs_s=/300x0:3540x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72838015/wallpaper.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;Aftermath&lt;em>; 徽标。&lt;/em>; |图片：Aftermath&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;他们创建了 Aftermath，一个关于视频游戏和文化的新网站。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2023/11/7/23949269/aftermath-video-games-kotaku-defector&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949269/aftermath-video-games-kotaku-defector" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949269/aftermath-video-games-kotaku-defector</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry></feed>